story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_01: We won’t let you get away with this anymore!
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_02: Ugh! These Trainers might be trouble!
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_03:
Hmph. So that’s what those so-called sygna suits
look like?
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_05:
Oh, us? We’re the three commanders of
Team Galactic!
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_06:
We’ll crush anyone who even tries to get in
our way!
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_07: Hmph. You got us. You’re pretty strong.
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_09:
Oh, I remember you, kid. You’re that brat I beat
at Lake Acuity.
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_10: I hope you’re not still so laughably weak.
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_11:
Whatever. We don’t have to waste our time with
you right now.
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_16:
This man seems to be having a
terrible nightmare...
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_22:
Before I knew it, I was dreaming...and walking
around in this never-ending darkness...
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_23:
No matter how far I went, it was pitch-black
as far as I could see!
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_26:
We should investigate this phenomenon to figure
out what’s happening.
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_27: Could you tell Dawn and the others?
story_teamgalactic_01_06000/2401_1201_28:
I’m gonna follow Team Galactic before they
get away!
